{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"PointerEvent.height","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/height","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Pointer_events\">Pointer events</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><em><code>height</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/isPrimary\"><code>isPrimary</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pointerId\"><code>pointerId</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pointerType\"><code>pointerType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/pressure\"><code>pressure</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tangentialPressure\"><code>tangentialPressure</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltX\"><code>tiltX</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/tiltY\"><code>tiltY</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/twist\"><code>twist</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/getCoalescedEvents\"><code>getCoalescedEvents()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\"><code>MouseEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/UIEvent\"><code>UIEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Pointer Events に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/releasePointerCapture\"><code>Element.releasePointerCapture()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/setPointerCapture\"><code>Element.setPointerCapture()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.ongotpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.onlostpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/maxTouchPoints\"><code>Navigator.maxTouchPoints</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent\"><code>PointerEvent</code></a> インターフェイスの <strong><code>height</code></strong> 読み取り専用プロパティは、y 軸に沿ったポインタの接触ジオメトリの高さを表します（CSS ピクセル単位）。</span> ポインタデバイスのソース（指など）によっては、特定のポインタに対して、各イベントが異なる値を生成することがあります。</p>\n\n<p>入力ハードウェアが接触ジオメトリをブラウザーに報告できない場合、高さのデフォルトは <code>1</code> です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>contactHeight</em> = <em>pointerEvent</em>.height;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"contactheight\"><code>contactHeight</code></dt>\n <dd>イベントの接触面積の高さ（CSS ピクセル単位）。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>このプロパティの例は、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/width#example\">PointerEvent.width の例</a>に含まれています。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/pointerevents2/#widl-PointerEvent-height\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Pointer Events – Level 2<br><small lang=\"ja\">height の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">勧告</span></td>\n   <td>不安定版</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/pointerevents1/#widl-PointerEvent-height\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Pointer Events<br><small lang=\"ja\">height の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">廃止</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.PointerEvent.height","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/height/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"PointerEvent インターフェイスの height 読み取り専用プロパティは、y 軸に沿ったポインタの接触ジオメトリの高さを表します（CSS ピクセル単位）。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PointerEvent.height","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/pointerevent/height","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/pointerevent/height/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent","title":"PointerEvent"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PointerEvent/height","title":"PointerEvent.height"}],"pageTitle":"PointerEvent.height - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}